"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104uhw1665703037632.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uhw1665703037632.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uhw1665703037632.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"uhw1665703037632\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Full Name\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property contains the name of the Development Object, fully-qualified by the names of its parent or associated objects. Read only.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uhw1665703037632__section_kcp_nh3_nwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d892992e51\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uhw1665703037632__p_d97097e1_d97098e1_d97099e1\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Full Name</span> uniquely identifies\n        the Development Object in contexts outside the data structure but with the Main Development\n        Object.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uhw1665703037632__section_s3h_4h3_nwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d892992e63\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"uhw1665703037632__ul_rs3_ph3_nwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uhw1665703037632__li_d39440e1_d39441e1_d39442e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lym1665702585074.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lym1665702585074.html\" title=\"A Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in an Entity. This could represent a column in a DBMS table or data that is not stored in the database, such as a derived field or a user interface control. Its associated properties define the way it is stored, its GUI representation, and default behavior.\">Field</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uhw1665703037632__li_d39443e1_d39444e1_d39445e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wyt1665702609153.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyt1665702609153.html\" title=\"A Label is a Development Object that contains text that appears on a presentation component. Labels have properties, but most cannot be set dynamically.\">Label</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uhw1665703037632__li_d39446e1_d39447e1_d39448e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vuv1665702701508.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vuv1665702701508.html\" title=\"A Key is a Development Object that designates a field or combination of fields as a Primary Key, Candidate Key, or Index.\">Key</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uhw1665703037632__li_d39449e1_d39450e1_d39451e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xtb1665702702029.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xtb1665702702029.html\" title=\"A Relationship is a Development Object that represents an association between one entity and another. It specifies the primary or candidate keys to be used in maintaining the association, as well as the delete constraints to be used when deleting occurrences in the related entities.\">Relationship</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616301\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616301\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Full Name Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 01, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Full Name This property contains the name of the Development Object, fully-qualified by the names of its parent or associated objects. Read only. Description The Full Name uniquely identifies the Development Object in contexts outside the data structure but with the Main Development Object. Applies To Field Label Key Relationship Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}